{"tid":1560963,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(有圖) 蒙面法 咁伊斯蘭蒙面女性點算？","createTime":"2019-09-11T12:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T09:43:51.000Z","uid":222970,"like":77,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"263c628ed42145532767f01a94cbb0884d8514fe","tid":1560963,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:00:33.000Z","msg":"有冇人開始信奉真主 想蒙面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時d黑警會唔會一野扯爛穆斯林教徒d面罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chiGct7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchiGct7.jpg&h=a3ed3a22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/76cjJAN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F76cjJAN.jpg&h=ade848e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6738d00e4ae4d97193eae975eba6f2f9f6feff0","tid":1560963,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:01:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0pEqbc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0pEqbc4.png&h=1f16fd8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=6bb15e71\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond</a><br />\n<br />\n任何國際之間既債務都有繼承義務<br />\n慈禧簽果條辛丑條約 一戰果時民國繼續還<br />\n仲要還到1938年因爲打二戰窮到pk<br />\n去求條約國唔追辛丑賠款先可以停<br />\n既然中共自稱滿清正統承繼人<br />\n呢張債券自然本利點都要還<br />\n唔還既佢講乜差野要用南京條約去收番香港<br />\n而且美國政府係未同中共追還錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjpU2AG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t